title: I have scored 620 marks in the NEET 2020. What will be my All India Rank? - Quora

response.answer_text: Congratulations for your score in neet 2020.This is very difficult to predict rank in neet 2020.You are in safe zone and definitely you will get Govt.medical college. So enjoy and wait for official result.Do not be panic.Best of luck for your future ahead👍.
